The organisation wants the communities around the Polihali Dam site to be compensated for their land before construction of the project begins and to get perpetual royalties. 

Lesotho Highlands Water Project is a multi-phased project initiated to provide water for Gauteng province in South Africa and to generate hydro-electricity for Lesotho.  

To discuss this further, Samora Mangesi spoke to Mothusi Seqhee, Spokesperson for the Seinoli Litgislation Centre.. --ChannelAfrica--